Private Optional _connectTimeout

_connectTimeout: any
  • Defined in wstransport.ts:80

The current connection timeout. If it times out, we've failed to connect and should try again.

We use any here because NodeJS returns a Timer and browser returns a number and one can't be cast to the other, despite their working interoperably.
